283
00:18:40,009 --> 00:18:40,888
Leather of excellent quality.

284
00:18:40,889 --> 00:18:42,008
Give me another blanket.

285
00:18:42,009 --> 00:18:43,009
Okay.

286
00:18:51,690 --> 00:18:53,008
