293
00:19:10,129 --> 00:19:11,529
Have you seen her?

294
00:19:11,530 --> 00:19:12,530
No.

295
00:19:15,330 --> 00:19:16,689
Have you seen her?

296
00:19:16,690 --> 00:19:18,008
No.

