00:19:18,009 --> 00:19:18,929
Have you seen her?

298
00:19:18,930 --> 00:19:19,930
No.

299
00:19:22,450 --> 00:19:23,289
Please enjoy it.

300
00:19:23,290 --> 00:19:24,290
Okay.

