311
00:19:51,249 --> 00:19:52,409
I don't know.

312
00:19:52,410 --> 00:19:53,888
The same with me, perhaps.

313
00:19:53,889 --> 00:19:55,169
You are not friends?

314
00:19:55,170 --> 00:19:56,768
Then why are you looking for her?

315
00:19:56,769 --> 00:19:58,569
Does she owe you money?

316
