335
00:20:53,450 --> 00:20:54,769
Are you from Chang'an?

336
00:21:05,249 --> 00:21:06,728
Liar!

337
00:21:06,729 --> 00:21:07,569
Lady... no, no...

338
00:21:07,570 --> 00:21:08,728
Swordswoman! Don't be angry.

339
00:21:08,729 --> 00:21:10,248
Just a misunderstanding.

340
00:21:10,249 --> 00:21:11,368
Was she killed by you?

341
00:21:11,369 --> 00:21:13,088
No, no. I am her friend.

342
00:21:13,089 --> 00:21:14,290
