343
00:21:15,570 --> 00:21:16,488
Friend?

344
00:21:16,489 --> 00:21:17,409
Yes, yes.

345
00:21:17,410 --> 00:21:18,690
We were in the same camp.

346
00:21:19,889 --> 00:21:20,889
