349
00:21:33,249 --> 00:21:37,769
I never thought that Young Master would have gone through this.

350
00:21:39,249 --> 00:21:41,128
Young Master had a good luck!

351
00:21:41,129 --> 00:21:42,728
She was captured by Ashile Tribe.

352
00:21:42,729 --> 00:21:44,689
She could even made them such a mess.

353
00:21:44,690 --> 00:21:46,488
Maybe not.

354
00:21:46,489 --> 00:21:47,489
What do you mean?

355
00:21:48,769 --> 00:21:50,209
We don't know if she is alive or not,

356
00:21:50,210 --> 00:21:51,810
so we don't know if she has a good luck.

357
00:21:54,729 --> 00:21:55,968
Believe me, Ms. Luo.

358
00:21:55,969 --> 00:21:59,449
People of Yanxing Sect have been looking for her too.

359
00:21:59,450 --> 00:22:01,809
We would finally find a way out.

360
00:22:01,810 --> 00:22:02,849
Yanxing Sect?

361
00:22:04,690 --> 00:22:09,728
We were the staff of the former governor of Shuozhou, Gongsun Heng.

362
00:22:09,729 --> 00:22:15,569
We are now following your master, and we are called Yanxing Sect.

363
00:22:15,570 --> 00:22:18,968
We pretend to be a trade caravan.

364
00:22:18,969 --> 00:22:20,849
You should believe us.

365
00:22:23,530 --> 00:22:26,969
More people would be of more power.

366
00:22:28,170 --> 00:22:32,930
It'd be hard for you to find her only by this drawing.

367
00:22:35,530 --> 00:22:36,530
Why?

368
00:22:39,330 --> 00:22:43,450
Anyway, we will look for her with you together.

369
00:22:44,810 --> 00:22:47,049
Ms. Luo, since we are for the same goal,

370
00:22:47,050 --> 00:22:50,488
we have to exchange our messages,

371
00:22:50,489 --> 00:22:53,689
so that we can work together to find Young Master.

372
00:22:53,690 --> 00:22:56,409
No matter who get the message first,

373
00:22:56,410 --> 00:23:00,609
we have to contact each other through these codes on this paper.

374
00:23:07,050 --> 00:23:08,690
Is that clear?

375
00:23:10,930 --> 00:23:13,690
Take this too.

376
00:23:30,050 --> 00:23:33,008
Miss, you'll be in danger if you go alone.

377
00:23:33,009 --> 00:23:34,170
Do you need my protection?

378
00:23:45,489 --> 00:23:46,489
Okay. Never mind.

379
00:23:55,930 --> 00:23:56,608
Situ Langlang!

380
00:23:56,609 --> 00:23:57,409
Is that enough?

381
00:23:57,410 --> 00:23:58,049
No! Not enough!

382
00:23:58,050 --> 00:23:59,169
Far away!

383
00:23:59,170 --> 00:24:00,569
Taoist Sun is my creditor.

384
00:24:00,570 --> 00:24:02,569
He asked me to train you to cure you.

385
00:24:02,570 --> 00:24:04,008
I have to listen to him.

386
00:24:04,009 --> 00:24:04,929
Cure?

387
00:24:04,930 --> 00:24:06,088
You call this a cure?

388
00:24:06,089 --> 00:24:06,728
Watch it!

389
00:24:06,729 --> 00:24:08,089
If you get hurt, it won't be good.

390
00:24:12,570 --> 00:24:13,488
Situ!

391
00:24:13,489 --> 00:24:16,089
Your apprentice is quite good!

392
00:24:17,369 --> 00:24:19,329
Stop, stop!

393
00:24:19,330 --> 00:24:21,049
What... what student?

394
00:24:21,050 --> 00:24:24,809
You take a long weapon, bullying a girl with no weapon.

395
00:24:24,810 --> 00:24:26,169
How could you say you are a swordsman?

396
00:24:26,170 --> 00:24:27,170
Bully you?

397
00:24:29,009 --> 00:24:31,008
Since you have to counter with me everyday,

398
00:24:31,009 --> 00:24:33,210
