399
00:24:34,489 --> 00:24:35,489
Of course I can.

400
00:24:54,650 --> 00:24:55,650
So what?

401
00:24:59,570 --> 00:25:00,289
Why you...

402
00:25:00,290 --> 00:25:01,290
Again!

403
00:25:11,650 --> 00:25:12,529
How is it?

404
00:25:12,530 --> 00:25:13,530
Am I superior?

405
00:25:16,810 --> 00:25:19,249
Little girl, would you like to be my apprentice?

406
00:25:20,489 --> 00:25:21,968
We are at the same age.

407
00:25:21,969 --> 00:25:23,330
I won't take you as my master.

408
00:25:24,769 --> 00:25:26,169
Don't say it.

409
00:25:26,170 --> 00:25:28,289
It's been hard for me to find an apprentice.

410
00:25:28,290 --> 00:25:29,488
Think about it.

411
00:25:29,489 --> 00:25:32,289
Yue Maiden's Swordsmanship has to be inherited.

412
00:25:32,290 --> 00:25:36,329
If I learn it, can I conquer all enemies,

413
00:25:36,330 --> 00:25:38,529
and kill all the enemies in the battlefield?

414
00:25:38,530 --> 00:25:40,529
Of course, so easy.

415
00:25:40,530 --> 00:25:44,329
If it's true, if you can help me with my revenge,

416
00:25:44,330 --> 00:25:45,890
then I'd like to take you as my master.

417
00:25:52,369 --> 00:25:53,049
Forget it.

418
00:25:53,050 --> 00:25:53,848
I won't do it.

419
00:25:53,849 --> 00:25:54,929
You didn't hear it.

420
00:25:54,930 --> 00:25:56,209
Wait!

421
00:25:56,210 --> 00:25:58,128
You haven't taught me. How do you know that I can't?

422
00:25:58,129 --> 00:26:00,329
I've heard from what you said.

423
00:26:00,330 --> 00:26:02,728
We are in a different world, you can't learn it.

424
00:26:02,729 --> 00:26:03,968
Don't waste our time.

425
00:26:03,969 --> 00:26:05,248
I don't believe it.

426
00:26:05,249 --> 00:26:07,848
You are so stubborn.

427
00:26:07,849 --> 00:26:11,169
Fine, I'll teach you.

428
00:26:11,170 --> 00:26:14,768
But you know what, you can't learn it.

429
00:26:14,769 --> 00:26:15,669
I'm Li Changge.

430
00:26:15,670 --> 00:26:17,390
Thanks for teaching me swordsmanship, Situ.

431
00:26:20,650 --> 00:26:21,650
Fine.

432
00:26:23,210 --> 00:26:27,608
She just recovered, so don't make her too tired.

433
00:26:27,609 --> 00:26:31,849
Grandpa... I also worked hard, why don't you care about me?

434
00:26:33,729 --> 00:26:37,968
Little girl, I have a student, he was asking me for a diagnosis.

435
00:26:37,969 --> 00:26:39,930
Would you come with us to Luoyang?

436
00:26:41,530 --> 00:26:42,530
Luoyang?

437
00:26:44,489 --> 00:26:46,289
