440
00:26:51,489 --> 00:26:56,169
If I didn't have you, I would already died.

441
00:26:56,170 --> 00:26:57,728
Don't say that.

442
00:26:57,729 --> 00:26:59,049
We will soon arrive in Luoyang.

443
00:26:59,050 --> 00:27:01,450
As soon as we arrive, I will find you a good doctor.

444
00:27:03,210 --> 00:27:04,449
Don't brag.

445
00:27:04,450 --> 00:27:07,368
