446
00:27:07,369 --> 00:27:08,529
Xiao Wu!

447
00:27:08,530 --> 00:27:10,608
Come on to my back.

448
00:27:10,609 --> 00:27:11,049
Come on.

449
00:27:11,050 --> 00:27:12,128
No, no.

450
00:27:12,129 --> 00:27:14,368
I am a strong man.

451
00:27:14,369 --> 00:27:16,449
