580
00:35:01,770 --> 00:35:06,128
I want to head to Luoyang and

581
00:35:06,129 --> 00:35:09,649
find someone more suitable for the position of Minister of War.

582
00:35:09,650 --> 00:35:11,048
Who is it?

583
00:35:11,049 --> 00:35:12,729
The abandoned talent of Sui dynasty.

584
00:35:12,730 --> 00:35:14,250
Li Jing, Li Yaoshi.

585
00:35:25,849 --> 00:35:28,170
Sister, have some rest.

586
00:35:30,490 --> 00:35:32,848
No, I'm okay.

587
00:35:32,849 --> 00:35:34,848
You can't even tell lies.

588
00:35:34,849 --> 00:35:36,289
